Package: rrais
Title: Tidy and Manipulate the Brazilian Employer-Employee Dataset
Version: 0.3.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Arthur", "Bazolli", email = "baarthur0@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    `rrais` offers a simple framework to clean and standardize data from RAIS, 
    the Brazilian employer-employee dataset. Now you don't need to worry about layout changes across 
    years, numbers incorrectly registered as characters, commas instead of dots, and so on!
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
